    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>drained cannellini beans </strong>and <strong>half </strong>of<strong> </strong>the <strong>smoked paprika </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) to the pan</p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until the pepper has softened – this is your <strong>chorizo mixture</strong></p>",
