    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining smoked paprika </strong>with the <strong>mayo </strong>and <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>(save the rest for later!) in a small bowl – this is your<strong> smoky mayo</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
