    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoky chorizo tortilla stacks </strong>with any<strong> remaining salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Pour the <strong>remaining white wine vinegar</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over the salad</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
